{
  "stem": "25209.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were just not, not very far at all, and my father grabbing me by the hand and pulling me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember I could not keep up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My legs just wouldn't go as fast as his.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was very weird, because I had to run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I couldn't run that fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think he half dragged me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He couldn't lift me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I was a big kid by the time I was seven or eight, maybe, seven-- so-- and then jumping into this, into this ditch.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, thank, thank goodness, we were safe again for a little minute.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But-- for a little while until next time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the, the-- this river of refugees-- and the Pole-- you know, the Polish army just gave in after a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were all fleeing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And everybody was going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember at night, it was dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was presumably asleep in the back of the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember this gray mass of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the, the Polish army-- there was a little bridge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we all wanted to cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because the-- because over the bridge was Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- but the Polish army wanted to get through that bridge, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my father revved up the car and just drove into the middle of this army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the, the, the officer there was furious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But he wouldn't stop the whole army to get rid of one refugee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because they weren't letting the refugees through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They wanted to save their own skin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So the refugees, the Jews, you know, and everybody else, they had to stay in the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I think they all perished, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's how we got to Korets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And from Korets, I have a very good memory about everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
